## How to work
Maximum 100 lines of change per request.  Prefer less.  If a request would require more than that, instead write a plan describing the change so we can work at smaller increments.

If a requested course of action seems inefficient, stop and propose a more efficient course.

Put non-trivial plans in a markdown file in doc/ so I can review.

Use Test Driven Development.
Write test - stop for review.  
Make test pass.  Stop for review.  
Refactor.  Stop for review.

Don't bother using git unless asked a history or status question.  I will take care of git.

